"6  medium Granny Smith apples, peeled and cut into eighths","1 tablespoon lemon juice","1/2 cup firmly packed dark brown sugar","1/2 cup chopped walnuts","1/2 cup maple syrup","1/4 cup sweetened dried cranberries (we tested with Craisins)","1/4 cup butter, melted","2 teaspoons ground cinnamon","2 tablespoons water","1 tablespoon cornstarch"